	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Greetings Paladins,<br><br>I found this information on another Paladin web site.&nbsp;&nbsp;I didn't confirm any of the numbers but they look about right to me.<br><br>For those who wonder 'WHY' I keep singing the praises of the Mithril Two-handed Sword...just check the Damage per Minute stats below.<br><br>Keep in mind, if you already have a haste item, then other weapons begin to do more damage since the haste from the Mithril Two-handed sword doesn't stack with other haste items like the FBSS, etc. But if you DON'T have a haste item...the Mithril is very VERY hard to beat.<br><br>TWO HANDED WEAPONS<br><br>Soulfire 23/45<br>45th = 496 50th = 536 55th = 607 60th = 652 <br><br>Blade of Xalgoz 23/40<br>45th = 530 50th = 574 55th = 654 60th = 704 <br><br>Abram's Axe of the Stoic 30/48<br>45th = 570 50th = 608 55th = 680 60th = 725 <br><br>Argent Defender 33/49<br>45th = 609 50th = 647 55th = 719 60th = 766 <br><br>Nathsar 17/30<br>45th = 560 50th = 618 55th = 718 60th = 778 <br><br>Arbitor's Combine 30/43<br>45th = 624 50th = 666 55th = 746 60th = 796 <br><br>Axe of Lost Souls 30/40<br>45th = 648 50th = 693 55th = 778 60th = 832 <br><br>Mithril Two-hander 21/40<br>45th = 646 50th = 703 55th = 804 60th = 867 <br><br>Fiery Avenger 33/44<br>45th = 694 50th = 735 55th = 817 60th = 869 <br><br>Nature's Defender 38/46<br>45th = 757 50th = 797 55th = 879 60th = 932 <br><br>Fiery Defender 35/40<br>45th = 785 50th = 831 55th = 922 60th = 980 <br><br>Kneesmasher Ayebulger<br>Dwarven Cavalier<br><br>&quot;Never Mistake Kindness for Weakness&quot;<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Kneesmasher Ayebulger<br>Dwarven Knight<br>Torvonnilous Server<br><br>"Never Mistake Kindness for Weakness"</td></tr>
